gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 130, Bucks 111
gameRecap.excerpt: The Raptors defeated the Bucks, 130-111. Pascal Siakam recorded 26 points, seven assists, and six rebounds for the Raptors, while Dennis Schroder added 24 points and 11 assists in the victory. Malik Beasley tallied 20 points, two rebounds, and two assists for the Bucks in the losing effort. The Raptors improve to 2-3 on the season, while the Bucks fall to 2-2.
